'S e iomall-baile [[Glaschu|Ghlaschu]] a tha ann an Robroyston. Tha e suidhichte air àird an earra-thuath a’ bhaile.

'S e sin an t-àite far an deach [[Uilleam Uallas]] a ghlacadh [[5 an Lùnasdal]] [[1305]]. 
An diugh tha clach-chuimhneachan ri faicinn an seo le soidhne sgrìobhte ann an [[Laideann]]: 
<blockquote>Dico tibi verum, libertas optimum rerum,<br>nunquam servili sub nexu, vivito fili<br> (''I tell you the truth, the best of all things is freedom,<br>never son, live under the bonds of slavery'')</blockquote> 
'S e sin am facal-suaicheantais a dh’ ionnsaich Uallas bhon athair aige nuair a bha e òg.


